
Overview of noun half

The noun half has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                           
1. (42) one-half, half -- (one of two equal parts of a divisible whole; "half a loaf"; "half an hour"; "a century and one half")
2. half -- (one of two divisions into which some games or performances are divided: the two divisions are separated by an interval)

